/facebook/react-native/labels/CLA%20Signed","name":"CLA Signed","color":"ffffff","default":false,"description":"This label is managed by the Facebook bot. Authors need to sign the CLA before a PR can be reviewed."}],"state":"open","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":3,"created_at":"2020-11-24T14:00:01Z","updated_at":"2020-11-24T14:30:56Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"NONE","active_lock_reason":null,"pull_request":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/facebook/react-native/pulls/30466","html_url":"https://github.com/facebook/react-native/pull/30466","diff_url":"https://github.com/facebook/react-native/pull/30466.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/facebook/react-native/pull/30466.patch"},"body":"<!-- Thanks for submitting a pull request! We appreciate you spending the time to work on these changes. Please provide enough information so that others can review your pull request. The three fields below are mandatory. -->\r\n\r\n## Summary\r\n\r\n`Pressable` does not support foreground Android ripples: https://reactnative.dev/docs/touchablenativefeedback#useforeground\r\n\r\nThis is needed for certain scenarios otherwise `Pressable` cannot be used, and users have to resort to `TouchableNativeFeedback` instead.\r\n\r\n`foreground` is necessary when using `react-native-linear-gradient` for example, otherwise the ripple renders underneath the gradient and if used for buttons, it doesn't show any feedback.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/react-native-linear-gradient/react-native-linear-gradient/issues/64\r\n\r\n<!-- Explain the **motivation** for making this change. What existing problem does the pull request solve? -->\r\n\r\n## Changelog\r\n\r\n[Android] [Added] Pressable: Add foreground prop to android_ripple\r\n\r\n\r\n## Test Plan\r\n\r\nWith `foreground: true`:\r\n\r\n![M2bx2dILpj](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/697707/100103253-50fcf480-2e6d-11eb-8863-c4dd3b524d76.gif)\r\n\r\nAlso, here's a different example of using `foreground` `true/false`:\r\n\r\n`foreground: false` (default):\r\n![Tqb6REqXyC](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/697707/100103703-eb5d3800-2e6d-11eb-9788-70ddd5a6b903.gif)\r\n\r\n`foreground: true` (new):\r\n![4hv3UVFs1d](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/697707/100103763-03cd5280-2e6e-11eb-8b48-9b4011e2ee37.gif)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<!-- Demonstrate the code is solid. Example: The exact commands you ran and their output, screenshots / videos if the pull request changes the user interface. -->\r\n","performed_via_github_app":null},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/facebook/react-native/issues/30465","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/facebook/react-native","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/facebook/react-native/issues/30465/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/facebook/react-native/issues/30465/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/facebook/react-native/issues/30465/events","html_url":"https://github.com/facebook/react-native/issues/30465","id":749273650,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU3NDkyNzM2NTA=","number":30465,"title":"[TouchableNativeFeedback, Button] onPress triggered even when touch re-entered component ","user":{"login":"darron1217","id":8064923,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjgwNjQ5MjM=","avatar_url":"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/8064923?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/darron1217","html_url":"https://github.com/darron1217","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/darron1217/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/darron1217/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/darron1217/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/darron1217/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/darron1217/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/darron1217/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/darron1217/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/darron1