 Platforms: iOS 13.6, DriverKit 19.0, macOS 10.15, tvOS 13.4, watchOS 6.2\r\n    Android SDK: Not Found\r\n  IDEs:\r\n    Android Studio: 4.0 AI-193.6911.18.40.6626763\r\n    Xcode: 11.6/11E708 - /usr/bin/xcodebuild\r\n  Languages:\r\n    Java: 11.0.8 - /usr/bin/javac\r\n    Python: 2.7.16 - /usr/bin/python\r\n  npmPackages:\r\n    @react-native-community/cli: Not Found\r\n    react: 16.13.1 => 16.13.1 \r\n    react-native: 0.63.3 => 0.63.3 \r\n    react-native-macos: Not Found\r\n  npmGlobalPackages:\r\n    *react-native*: Not Found\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Steps To Reproduce\r\nProvide a detailed list of steps that reproduce the issue.\r\n\r\n1. Create Button\r\n2. Press it and move your finger outside of component\r\n3. Re-Enter component and release finger.\r\n\r\n## Expected Results\r\nRe entering(dragging?) should not be regarded as `press`\r\n\r\n## Snack, code example, screenshot, or link to a repository:\r\nAbove","performed_via_github_app":null},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/facebook/react-native/issues/30464","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/facebook/react-native","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/facebook/react-native/issues/30464/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/facebook/react-native/issues/30464/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/facebook/react-native/issues/30464/events","html_url":"https://github.com/facebook/react-native/issues/30464","id":749271832,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU3NDkyNzE4MzI=","number":30464,"title":"Keyboard focus (from a physical keyboard) won't enter TextInput fields on Tab/Shift+Tab in Android","user":{"login":"NatPri","id":25355689,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI1MzU1Njg5","avatar_url":"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/25355689?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/NatPri","html_url":"https://github.com/NatPri","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/NatPri/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/NatPri/following{/other_user}","